<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="container my-4">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <section id="about-us">
            <p>Welcome to ChatApp, the ultimate platform for real-time communication! Our mission is to provide a seamless and engaging chat experience for users around the world. Whether you're connecting with friends, collaborating with colleagues, or meeting new people, ChatApp has you covered.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="contact-us" class="my-4">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>We value your feedback and are here to help you. If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to reach out to us:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Email: support@chatapp.com</li>
                <li>Phone: +1-800-123-4567</li>
                <li>Address: 123 ChatApp Lane, Communicopolis, CA 90210</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="faq" class="my-4">
            <h2>FAQ</h2>
            <h3>How do I create a new account?</h3>
            <p>Click on the "Register" button on the home page and follow the instructions to create your account.</p>
            <h3>How can I reset my password?</h3>
            <p>If you've forgotten your password, click the "Forgot Password" link on the login page and follow the instructions.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="privacy-policy" class="my-4">
            <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>Your privacy is important to us. At ChatApp, we use state-of-the-art security measures to protect your personal information. We employ encryption techniques such as AES (Advanced Encryption Standard) to secure your data during transmission and storage. Additionally, we use SSL (Secure Sockets Layer) to ensure secure connections between your browser and our servers. Rest assured, we are committed to safeguarding your information and maintaining your privacy.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
